Download the free Scala program from http://www.huygens-fokker.org/scala/ and install it on your computer. 
This is 1 program in which you can write your own scales. According to him, there are 4000 scales worldwide which differ from the classic European tone and sine scale. 
The program is difficult to learn because it requires a lot of knowledge on music theory but we will be limited to what is needed to compose the Byzantine scales.
